WEBVTT

00:00.042 --> 00:03.003
<i>Previously on Underground...
She ain't comin' with us.</i>

00:07.850 --> 00:09.916
Slavery ain't just a sin,

00:09.952 --> 00:11.284
it's a state of war.

00:12.087 --> 00:14.120
You want to be a nigger?

00:14.156 --> 00:15.822
'Cause I will brand you like one.

00:16.992 --> 00:18.225
<i>Massas is worried about</i>

00:18.260 --> 00:20.861
<i>somebody named John Brown
stealin' slaves.</i>

00:20.896 --> 00:22.028
If there was a map

00:22.064 --> 00:24.197
<i>to all the safe houses
on the Underground...</i>

00:24.233 --> 00:25.298
There is.

00:25.334 --> 00:26.334
We've got cargo.

